text: Eoin O'Mahony may refer to: * Eoin "the Pope" O'Mahony (1904–1970) Irish barrister, activist, genealogist, and raconteur * Eoin O'Mahony (Gaelic football) (born 1962) member of the 1989 Cork All-Ireland senior football champion squad * List of people with locked-in syndrome#Eoin O'Mahony
